<item>
            <title>[SEC-1919] AuthenticationServiceException logged on DEBUG level</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1919</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When LDAP server is not available AuthenticationServiceException should be logged on the ERROR level not on DEBUG.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
